Jeff Immelt - Wikipedia






















 






Jeff Immelt

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Jeffrey R. Immelt)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Jeff Immelt








Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of General Electric



Incumbent



Assumed office
September 7, 2001


Preceded by
Jack Welch





Personal details


